In Isabella's words: \"Mason is a knave and David is a knight\". David remarked, \"Mason is a knight if and only if Isabella is a knave\". Olivia remarked, \"Benjamin is a knave and Michael is a knave\". So who is a knight and who is a knave?", "answer": "{\"Mason\": \"knave\", \"Michael\": \"knave\", \"Benjamin\": \"knave\", \"Jackson\": \"knave\", \"Isabella\": \"knave\", \"David\": \"knave\", \"Olivia\": \"knight\"}"}

Logan stated, \"Matthew is a knight and Ava is a knight\". \"David is a knight or Joseph is a knight,\" Matthew declared. So who is a knight and who is a knave?", "answer": "{\"Aiden\": \"knave\", \"David\": \"knight\", \"Evelyn\": \"knight\", \"Joseph\": \"knight\", \"Ava\": \"knight\", \"Logan\": \"knight\", \"Matthew\": \"knight\"}"}

As Jack put it, \"Evelyn is a knight if and only if Evelyn is a knave\". Amelia said that Jack is a knight or Jackson is a knave. In Abigail's words: \"If Jackson is a knave then Abigail is a knight\". So who is a knight and who is a knave?", "answer": "{\"Owen\": \"knave\", \"Aiden\": \"knight\", \"Evelyn\": \"knight\", \"Jackson\": \"knave\", \"Jack\": \"knave\", \"Amelia\": \"knight\", \"Abigail\": \"knight\"}"}

Ethan told you that Mason is a knight if and only if Jacob is a knight. \"If Mason is a knight then Jacob is a knight,\" William claimed. Jacob expressed that William is a knave.
